text: Viktor Lisitsyn (17 October 1926 - 20 December 1976) was a Soviet equestrian. He competed in the individual jumping event at the 1972 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1926 births Category:1976 deaths Category:Soviet male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of the Soviet Union Category:Equestrians at the 1972 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing
